---
import { IconArrowUpRight } from "@tabler/icons-react"
---

<div class="gap-2 grid md:grid-cols-2">
    <article class="space-y-2 md:gap-6 border border-gray-border p-3 rounded-md group cursor-pointer hover:bg-[#ffffff05] transition-all duration-300">
        <h3 class="flex items-center justify-between text-lg text-color-primary">
            <span class="font-semibold">
                Mesa de ayuda
            </span>
            <IconArrowUpRight className="transition-all duration-300 group-hover:translate-x-[2px] -translate-y-[2px] text-color-subtle group-hover:text-color-primary" width={16} />
        </h3>
        <img src="imgs/proyectos/mesaDeAyuda.webp" alt="" class="rounded-md">
        <div class="flex flex-col justify-between">
            <div class="mb-4">
                <p class="mt-2 text-pretty text-color-secondary text-sm">
                    Sistema interno con panel administrativo, desarrollado para <strong>agilizar la resolución de problemas</strong> sin necesidad de intervención técnica, cuenta con un <strong>buscador inteligente</strong> y un <strong>sistema de tickets</strong>.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1">
                <span class="transition-all flex items-center text-xs text-color-secondary border-gray-border space-x-2  rounded-md border px-2.5 py-1">
                    Angular
                </span>
                <span class="transition-all flex items-center text-xs text-color-secondary border-gray-border space-x-2  rounded-md border px-2.5 py-1">
                    TypeScript
                </span>
                <span class="transition-all flex items-center text-xs text-color-secondary border-gray-border space-x-2 rounded-md border px-2.5 py-1">
                    Tailwind
                </span>
                <span class="transition-all flex items-center text-xs text-color-secondary border-gray-border space-x-2 rounded-md border px-2.5 py-1">
                    SQLite
                </span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </article>
    <article class="space-y-2 md:gap-6 border border-gray-border p-3 rounded-md group cursor-pointer hover:bg-[#ffffff05] transition-all duration-300">
        <h3 class="flex items-center justify-between gap-2 text-lg text-color-primary">
            <span class="font-semibold">
                VexaAnnounce
            </span>
            <IconArrowUpRight className="transition-all duration-300 group-hover:translate-x-[2px] -translate-y-[2px] text-color-subtle group-hover:text-color-primary" width={16} />
        </h3>
        <img src="imgs/proyectos/VexaAnnounce.webp" alt="" class="rounded-md">
        <div class="flex flex-col justify-between">
            <div class="mb-4">
                <p class="mt-2 text-pretty text-color-secondary text-sm">
                    Bot de Discord desarrollado para <strong>anunciar mensajes programados</strong>, generar tickets, programar el borrado de mensajes en canales y un <strong>sistema automático de moderación</strong>. 
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1">
                <span class="transition-all flex items-center text-xs text-color-secondary border-gray-border space-x-2  rounded-md border px-2.5 py-1">
                    JavaScript
                </span>
                <span class="transition-all flex items-center text-xs text-color-secondary border-gray-border space-x-2 rounded-md border px-2.5 py-1">
                    Node.js
                </span>
                <span class="transition-all flex items-center text-xs text-color-secondary border-gray-border space-x-2 rounded-md border px-2.5 py-1">
                    Discord.js
                </span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </article>
</div>